dr.inference.markovjumps
Class StateChange

java.lang.Object
  dr.inference.markovjumps.StateChange

public class StateChange
extends java.lang.Object

A class to represent a state-change in a continuous-time Markov chain. This class is equivalent to ColourChange in terms of parameters, but labels events more generically as either forward or backwards (instead of just backwards) in time.

TODO Remove dr.evolution.tree.ColourChange (wrong package)
